{"tid":989552,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遇全球最大大白鯊　潛水員海底共舞","createTime":"2019-01-21T02:57:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-24T14:14:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"869f1a84837ba8b250b5baae20bceeae9ff3e933","tid":989552,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T02:57:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190120/20595190\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190120%2F20595190&d=Hs94iRqvlNh70kCrbpu8%2BDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=6d24023d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190120%2F20595190&h=af235a88\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190120/20595190</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年01月20日 <br />\n<br />\n遇全球最大大白鯊　潛水員海底共舞<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190120/large/20wx3p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190120%2Flarge%2F20wx3p.jpg&h=2fad2af2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「深藍」與鯊魚專家的合照紅爆網絡。路透社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一對專門研究鯊魚的專家，日前在美國夏威夷遇上大白鯊，疑是有紀錄以來全球最大的50歲大白鯊「深藍」（Deep Blue），「人鯊共舞」合照在網上瘋傳，兩人藉此促政府通過護鯊保育條例。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n促夏威夷禁獵鯊<br />\n<br />\n在夏威夷歐胡島經營潛水生意和「觀鯊團」的拉姆齊（Ocean Ramsey），上周二與未婚夫奧莉芬特（Juan Oliphant）潛泳時發現身逾六米長的大白鯊徘徊在一條死去的抹香鯨旁「開餐」，估計是因為飢餓而罕有現身；大白鯊與兩人及兩人的小船擦身而過，身兼模特兒的拉姆齊亦游近與牠互動和合照，並將照片上載社交網。<br />\n<br />\n拉姆齊估計大白鯊出現，代表牠在附近水域有其他夥伴，以此力推夏威夷政府今年通過法案禁止獵鯊；她和大白鯊合照是為向大家說明鯊應該受保護，「鯊魚普遍不得同情，我們從傳媒看到的牠很兇殘，亦長得不可愛，但我們需要牠以保生態平衡」。不過她並不鼓勵新手仿效其做法，尤其當鯊魚在大快朵頤的時候。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社/路透社  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n開16槍射殺黑人青年　美白人警判監七年"},{"pid":"b9a987c1dfb92124f6dff9caa2dc1b32880c67f7","tid":989552,"uid":1672,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T03:08:44.000Z","msg":"俾條大白鯊食撚左就好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59afdb395234324be30d4514f6f84dba1d63d1f1","tid":989552,"uid":74728,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T03:13:53.000Z","msg":"開16槍射殺黑人青年　美白人警判監七年 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 七年"},{"pid":"813154d8a928996c8f9a10705e2cddee5bdc2651","tid":989552,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9a987c1dfb92124f6dff9caa2dc1b32880c67f7","tid":989552,"uid":1672,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T03:08:44.000Z","msg":"俾條大白鯊食撚左就好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T03:14:19.000Z","msg":"成班潛水員跟本睇住佢食飽先埋去影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"354ebf4fe058d82815a08a2a94b35e9802f5aff3","tid":989552,"uid":108467,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T03:17:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SzmiYVy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSzmiYVy.png&h=99d092bc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d6e5490d1e10f5cedfe1188cb054b0b3275d1394","tid":989552,"uid":62247,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"813154d8a928996c8f9a10705e2cddee5bdc2651","tid":989552,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9a987c1dfb92124f6dff9caa2dc1b32880c67f7","tid":989552,"uid":1672,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T03:08:44.000Z","msg":"俾條大白鯊食撚左就好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T03:14:19.000Z","msg":"成班潛水員跟本睇住佢食飽先埋去影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T03:18:35.000Z","msg":"不過她並不鼓勵新手仿效其做法，尤其當鯊魚在大快朵頤的時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9180aa9eb33b5b1955812dcb4f33158093339959","tid":989552,"uid":81598,"like":5,"dislike